billyBob
.EE
.SS Set alias
Given a sample.yml file of:
.IP
.EX
b\f[B]:\f[R] &meow purr
a\f[B]:\f[R] cat
.EE
.PP
then
.IP
.EX
yq \(aq.a alias = \(dqmeow\(dq\(aq sample.yml
.EE
.PP
will output
.IP
.EX
b\f[B]:\f[R] &meow purr
a\f[B]:\f[R] *meow
.EE
.SS Set alias to blank does nothing
Given a sample.yml file of:
.IP
.EX
b\f[B]:\f[R] &meow purr
a\f[B]:\f[R] cat
.EE
.PP
then
.IP
.EX
yq \(aq.a alias = \(dq\(dq\(aq sample.yml
.EE
.PP
will output
.IP
.EX
b\f[B]:\f[R] &meow purr
a\f[B]:\f[R] cat
.EE
.SS Set alias relatively using assign\-update
Given a sample.yml file of:
.IP
.EX
b\f[B]:\f[R] &meow purr
a\f[B]:\f[R]
  f\f[B]:\f[R] meow
.EE
.PP
then
.IP
.EX
yq \(aq.a alias |= .f\(aq sample.yml
.EE
.PP
will output
