.EE
.SS Explode with alias keys
Given a sample.yml file of:
.IP
.EX
f\f[B]:\f[R]
  a\f[B]:\f[R] &a cat
  *a \f[B]:\f[R] b
.EE
.PP
then
.IP
.EX
yq \(aqexplode(.f)\(aq sample.yml
.EE
