.SS Exploding inline merge anchor
Set \f[CR]\-\-yaml\-fix\-merge\-anchor\-to\-spec=true\f[R] to get this
correct merge behaviour (flag will default to true in late 2025).
.PP
Given a sample.yml file of:
.IP
.EX
a\f[B]:\f[R]
  b\f[B]:\f[R] &b 42
!!merge <<\f[B]:\f[R]
  c\f[B]:\f[R] *b
.EE
