.EE
.SS Traversing arrays by index
Given a sample.yml file of:
.IP
.EX
\f[B]\-\f[R] 1
\f[B]\-\f[R] 2
\f[B]\-\f[R] 3
.EE
.PP
then
.IP
.EX
yq \(aq.[0]\(aq sample.yml
.EE
