.EE
.SS Traversing nested arrays by index
Given a sample.yml file of:
.IP
.EX
\f[B][[],\f[R] \f[B][\f[R]cat\f[B]]]\f[R]
.EE
.PP
then
.IP
.EX
yq \(aq.[1][0]\(aq sample.yml
.EE
.PP
will output
.IP
.EX
