.EE
.SS Maps with numeric keys
Given a sample.yml file of:
.IP
.EX
2\f[B]:\f[R] cat
.EE
.PP
then
.IP
.EX
yq \(aq.[2]\(aq sample.yml
.EE
.PP
will output
.IP
.EX
