.EE
.SS Maps with non existing numeric keys
Given a sample.yml file of:
.IP
.EX
a\f[B]:\f[R] b
.EE
.PP
then
.IP
.EX
yq \(aq.[0]\(aq sample.yml
.EE
.PP
will output
.IP
.EX
