.EE
.SS Traversing merge anchors
Given a sample.yml file of:
.IP
.EX
foo\f[B]:\f[R] &foo
  a\f[B]:\f[R] foo_a
  thing\f[B]:\f[R] foo_thing
  c\f[B]:\f[R] foo_c
bar\f[B]:\f[R] &bar
  b\f[B]:\f[R] bar_b
  thing\f[B]:\f[R] bar_thing
  c\f[B]:\f[R] bar_c
foobarList\f[B]:\f[R]
  b\f[B]:\f[R] foobarList_b
  !!merge <<\f[B]:\f[R]
    \f[B]\-\f[R] *foo
    \f[B]\-\f[R] *bar
  c\f[B]:\f[R] foobarList_c
foobar\f[B]:\f[R]
  c\f[B]:\f[R] foobar_c
  !!merge <<\f[B]:\f[R] *foo
  thing\f[B]:\f[R] foobar_thing
.EE
.PP
then
.IP
.EX
yq \(aq.foobar.a\(aq sample.yml
.EE
.PP
will output
.IP
.EX
foo_a
.EE
