then
.IP
.EX
yq \-oy \(aq.\(aq sample.toml
.EE
.PP
will output
.IP
.EX
person\f[B]:\f[R]
  name\f[B]:\f[R] hello
  address\f[B]:\f[R] 12 cat st
.EE
.SS Encode: Scalar
Given a sample.toml file of:
.IP
.EX
person.name = \(dqhello\(dq
person.address = \(dq12 cat st\(dq
.EE
.PP
then
.IP
.EX
yq \(aq.person.name\(aq sample.toml
.EE
