  first\f[B]:\f[R] Tom
  last\f[B]:\f[R] Preston\-Werner
.EE
.SS Parse: Array Table
Given a sample.toml file of:
.IP
.EX

\f[B][owner.contact]\f[R]
name = \(dqTom Preston\-Werner\(dq
age = 36

\f[B][[owner.addresses]]\f[R]
