    \f[B]\-\f[R] street\f[B]:\f[R] second street
      suburb\f[B]:\f[R] nice
.EE
.SS Parse: Array of Array Table
Given a sample.toml file of:
.IP
.EX

\f[B][[fruits]]\f[R]
